          <li><strong>$0 — Free native</strong> — Google Business Profile dashboard, Canva Free. All effort, no spend.</li>
          <li><strong>$10–$30 — Schedulers + optimizers</strong> — Publer, OneUp, Circleboom, Localo, Local Falcon.</li>
          <li><strong>$30–$50 — Audit + done-for-you</strong> — BrightLocal, theStacc Local SEO. Tools that move ranking and save real time.</li>
          <li><strong>$50–$100 — Multi-tool bundles</strong> — BrightLocal + Local Falcon + Moz Local. Agency-ready without enterprise pricing.</li>
        </ol>

