          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ The "free is cheaper" trap</div>
          <p>Free GBP tools cost you in time, not dollars. Our 90-day benchmark showed single-location operators spent 8–12 hours per month on manual GBP. At even $25/hour of owner time, that is <strong>$200–$300/month of hidden cost</strong>. A $29 tool that drops you to 3 hours, or a $49 done-for-you tool that drops you to 20 minutes, beats "free" inside 30 days.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="how-we-tested">How we tested all 10 tools</h2>
        <p>Same 5 profiles, same KPIs, same 90-day window.</p>

