          <li><strong>Test profiles</strong> — 5 single-location GBPs across legal, dental, salon, gym, and HVAC.</li>
          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — set each tool to deliver weekly posts at minimum, track rank weekly, log all manual touches.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — total monthly cost (tool + time at $25/hr), impressions lift, calls, direction requests.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $820 across 10 tools, Mar–May 2026.</li>
        </ul>

